<br>
Sure, the warriors take a lot of punishment. Let them. Those who lack the necessary training deserved to be pummeled like whipping boys in a school playground.<br>
<br>
And what of this bard, Sophitya? A bastard half-elf. Father probably long since gone, leaving her elven mother abandoned and shunned in Kelethin. Still, she seems to be a capable fighter, and her music is something of a mystery to me. Not quite as powerful as the arcane, nor as divine as the workings of the priest.<br>
<br>
Watch her. Whistling a tune of war as she fights. Sun gleaming off her plate mail armor. Damn this cough! Fkahiras told me the Trials would be demanding, but I wouldn't listen. &quot;Ryhith,&quot; he said. &quot;Be forewarned. The trials are dangerous, and few have survived.&quot; I'm sure the bard thinks this Tier'Dal wizard is just crazy. No one ever understands the ability needed to use these spells....<br>
<br>
I must be moving along. I shall keep an eye on this...Sophitya. I'll have to make a point to meet her from time to time. Strength not withstanding.... <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub76.ezboard.com/frandomactsmemberinformation.showPrevMessage?topicID=238.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub76.ezboard.com/frandomactsmemberinformation.showNextMessage?topicID=238.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub76.ezboard.com/frandomactsmemberinformation.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=238.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/sunset/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub76.ezboard.com/frandomactsmemberinformation.emailToFriend?topicID=238.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub76.ezboard.com/frandomactsmemberinformation.threadControl?topicID=238.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/sunset/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub76.ezboard.com/frandomactsmemberinformation.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=238.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub76.ezboard.com/frandomactsmemberinformation.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=238.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub76.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="randomactsgeneraldiscussion">Guild Roundtable<option value="randomactsmemberinf